ames IV of Scotland and ruled as regent there after his death.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."]},{"name":"Margarete","meanings":["from Greek.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretha","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]}]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1353272,"age":3,"year":"1060","julianDay":2108217,"description":"Svend II forms Danish church.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Margrethe Sunesdatter was born in Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Denmark as the daughter of Sune Skjalmsen. She had at least 2 sons and 1 daughter with Herlog. She died on 25 October 1176, in Denmark."},"et":{"–25 October 1176":"–25. oktoober 1176","–1176":"–1176","–Male":"Surnud","–1220":"–1220","–1150":"–1150","1. januar 1150":"1. jaanuar 1150","1220":"1220","1176":"1176","25 October 1176":"25. oktoober 1176","1150":"1150","1060":"1060","Denmark":"Taani","Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Denmark":"Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Taani"},"fi":{"–25 October 1176":"–25. lokakuuta 1176","–1176":"–1176","–Male":"Kuollut","–1220":"–1220","–1150":"–1150","1. januar 1150":"1. tammikuuta 1150","1220":"1220","1176":"1176","25 October 1176":"25. lokakuuta 1176","1150":"1150","1060":"1060","Denmark":"Tanska","Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Denmark":"Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Tanska"},"fr":{"–25 October 1176":"–25 octobre 1176","–1176":"–1176","–Male":"Décédé","–1220":"–1220","–1150":"–1150","1. januar 1150":"1 janvier 1150","1220":"1220","1176":"1176","25 October 1176":"25 octobre 1176","1150":"1150","1060":"1060","Denmark":"Danemark","Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Denmark":"Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Danemark","lifeSummary":"Margrethe Sunesdatter est née à Ølstykke, Frederiksborg, Danemark, fille de Sune Skjalmsen. Elle a eu au moins 2 fils et 1 fille avec Herlog. Elle est décédée le 25 octobre 1176, à Danemark."},"de":{"–25 October 1176":"–25. Oktober 1176","–1176":"–1176","–Male":"Verstorben","–1220":"–1220","–1150":"–1150","1. januar 1150":"1. Januar 1150","1220":"12